      "prompt": "请创建一个完整的 HTML5 游戏。游戏描述：创建一个贪食蛇游戏。\n                    \n重要技术要求：\n1. 单个 HTML 文件\n2. 使用 Canvas API\n3. Canvas 尺寸必须为 360x640 像素（9:16 竖屏比例）\n4. 在 JavaScript 中设置：canvas.width = 360; canvas.height = 640;\n5. 在 CSS 中设置：canvas { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }\n6. 包含完整游戏循环\n7. 有得分系统\n8. 确保有趣可玩\n\n只返回 HTML 代码，不要其他说明。",
      "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>贪食蛇游戏</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        body {\n            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .game-container {\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        \n        canvas {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            background: #0f0f23;\n        }\n        \n        .ui-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        \n        .score-display {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        \n        .score-value {\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            display: block;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .high-score {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .game-message {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.95);\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: white;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.3);\n            pointer-events: auto;\n            display: none;\n        }\n        \n        .game-message h2 {\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 28px;\n        }\n        \n        .game-message p {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        \n        .game-message button {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4fd1c5 0%, #38b2ac 100%);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            margin: 10px;\n            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;\n            font-family: inherit;\n        }\n        \n        .game-message button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.4);\n        }\n        \n        .controls-hint {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 20px;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n            font-size: 14px;\n            padding: 10px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"game-container\">\n        <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\" width=\"360\" height=\"640\"></canvas>\n        \n        <div class=\"ui-overlay\">\n            <div class=\"score-display\">\n                <div>得分</div>\n                <div class=\"score-value\" id=\"scoreValue\">0</div>\n                <div class=\"high-score\">最高分: <span id=\"highScoreValue\">0</span></div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"controls-hint\">\n                方向键移动 | 空格键暂停 | R键重新开始\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"game-message\" id=\"menuMessage\">\n            <h2>贪食蛇游戏</h2>\n            <p>使用方向键控制蛇的移动<br>吃掉食物来增长身体<br>避免撞到墙壁和自己</p>\n            <button id=\"startButton\">开始游戏</button>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"game-message\" id=\"gameOverMessage\">\n            <h2>游戏结束</h2>\n            <p>最终得分: <span id=\"finalScore\">0</span></p>\n            <p>最高分: <span id=\"finalHighScore\">0</span></p>\n            <button id=\"restartButton\">重新开始</button>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"game-message\" id=\"pauseMessage\">\n            <h2>游戏暂停</h2>\n            <p>按空格键继续游戏</p>\n            <button id=\"resumeButton\">继续游戏</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // 游戏常量\n        const CANVAS_WIDTH = 360;\n        const CANVAS_HEIGHT = 640;\n        const GRID_SIZE = 20;\n        const GRID_COUNT_X = Math.floor(CANVAS_WIDTH / GRID_SIZE);\n        const GRID_COUNT_Y = Math.floor(CANVAS_HEIGHT / GRID_SIZE);\n        \n        // 游戏状态\n        const GAME_STATES = {\n            MENU: 'menu',\n            PLAYING: 'playing',\n            PAUSED: 'paused',\n            GAMEOVER: 'gameover'\n        };\n        \n        // 方向\n        const DIRECTIONS = {\n            UP: { x: 0, y: -1 },\n            DOWN: { x: 0, y: 1 },\n            LEFT: { x: -1, y: 0 },\n            RIGHT: { x: 1, y: 0 }\n        };\n        \n        // 游戏变量\n        let canvas, ctx;\n        let gameState = GAME_STATES.MENU;\n        let snake = [];\n        let food = { x: 0, y: 0 };\n        let direction = DIRECTIONS.RIGHT;\n        let nextDirection = DIRECTIONS.RIGHT;\n        let score = 0;\n        let highScore = 0;\n        let lastUpdateTime = 0;\n        let updateInterval = 150; // 毫秒\n        let gameLoopId;\n        \n        // 初始化游戏\n        function init() {\n            canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\n            ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n            \n            // 加载最高分\n            highScore = parseInt(localStorage.getItem('snakeHighScore')) || 0;\n            document.getElementById('highScoreValue').textContent = highScore;\n            \n            // 设置事件监听器\n            document.addEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown);\n            document.getElementById('startButton').addEventListener('click', startGame);\n            document.getElementById('restartButton').addEventListener('click', startGame);\n            document.getElementById('resumeButton').addEventListener('click', resumeGame);\n            \n            // 显示菜单\n            showMessage('menuMessage');\n            \n            // 开始游戏循环\n            gameLoopId = requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏主循环\n        function gameLoop(timestamp) {\n            const deltaTime = timestamp - lastUpdateTime;\n            \n            if (gameState === GAME_STATES.PLAYING && deltaTime >= updateInterval) {\n                update(deltaTime);\n                lastUpdateTime = timestamp;\n            }\n            \n            render();\n            gameLoopId = requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 更新游戏逻辑\n        function update(deltaTime) {\n            // 更新方向\n            direction = nextDirection;\n            \n            // 移动蛇\n            moveSnake();\n            \n            // 检查碰撞\n            if (checkCollision()) {\n                gameOver();\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            // 检查是否吃到食物\n            if (checkFoodCollision()) {\n                eatFood();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 移动蛇\n        function moveSnake() {\n            // 创建新的头部\n            const head = { ...snake[0] };\n            head.x += direction.x;\n            head.y += direction.y;\n            \n            // 将新头部添加到蛇身前面\n            snake.unshift(head);\n            \n            // 移除尾部（除非吃到食物）\n            if (!checkFoodCollision()) {\n                snake.pop();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 检查碰撞\n        function checkCollision() {\n            const head = snake[0];\n            \n            // 检查墙壁碰撞\n            if (head.x < 0 || head.x >= GRID_COUNT_X || head.y < 0 || head.y >= GRID_COUNT_Y) {\n                return true;\n            }\n            \n            // 检查自身碰撞（从第二个身体部分开始检查）\n            for (let i = 1; i < snake.length; i++) {\n                if (head.x === snake[i].x && head.y === snake[i].y) {\n                    return true;\n                }\n            }\n            \n            return false;\n        }\n        \n        // 检查食物碰撞\n        function checkFoodCollision() {\n            const head = snake[0];\n            return head.x === food.x && head.y === food.y;\n        }\n        \n        // 吃食物\n        function eatFood() {\n            // 增加分数\n            score += 10;\n            document.getElementById('scoreValue').textContent = score;\n            \n            // 更新最高分\n            if (score > highScore) {\n                highScore = score;\n                localStorage.setItem('snakeHighScore', highScore);\n                document.getElementById('highScoreValue').textContent = highScore;\n            }\n            \n            // 生成新食物\n            generateFood();\n            \n            // 加快游戏速度\n            if (updateInterval > 50) {\n                updateInterval -= 2;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 生成食物\n        function generateFood() {\n            let newFood;\n            let isOnSnake;\n            \n            do {\n                isOnSnake = false;\n                newFood = {\n                    x: Math.floor(Math.random() * GRID_COUNT_X),\n                    y: Math.floor(Math.random() * GRID_COUNT_Y)\n                };\n                \n                // 检查食物是否生成在蛇身上\n                for (const segment of snake) {\n                    if (segment.x === newFood.x && segment.y === newFood.y) {\n                        isOnSnake = true;\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            } while (isOnSnake);\n            \n            food = newFood;\n        }\n        \n        // 渲染游戏\n        function render() {\n            // 清空画布\n            ctx.fillStyle = '#0f0f23';\n            ctx.fillRect(0, 0, CANVAS_WIDTH, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            \n            // 绘制网格（可选，提供视觉参考）\n            drawGrid();\n            \n            // 绘制食物\n            drawFood();\n            \n            // 绘制蛇\n            drawSnake();\n            \n            // 绘制边界\n            drawBoundary();\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制网格\n        function drawGrid() {\n            ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)';\n            ctx.lineWidth = 1;\n            \n            for (let x = 0; x <= CANVAS_WIDTH; x += GRID_SIZE) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(x, 0);\n                ctx.lineTo(x, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n            \n            for (let y = 0; y <= CANVAS_HEIGHT; y += GRID_SIZE) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(0, y);\n                ctx.lineTo(CANVAS_WIDTH, y);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制蛇\n        function drawSnake() {\n            snake.forEach((segment, index) => {\n                const x = segment.x * GRID_SIZE;\n                const y = segment.y * GRID_SIZE;\n                \n                // 蛇头使用不同颜色\n                if (index === 0) {\n                    ctx.fillStyle = '#4fd1c5';\n                    ctx.shadowColor = '#4fd1c5';\n                    ctx.shadowBlur = 10;\n                } else {\n                    // 蛇身渐变\n                    const gradient = ctx.createLinearGradient(x, y, x + GRID_SIZE, y + GRID_SIZE);\n                    gradient.addColorStop(0, '#38b2ac');\n                    gradient.addColorStop(1, '#319795');\n                    ctx.fillStyle = gradient;\n                    ctx.shadowBlur = 0;\n                }\n                \n                // 绘制圆角矩形\n                drawRoundedRect(x + 1, y + 1, GRID_SIZE - 2, GRID_SIZE - 2, 4);\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 重置阴影\n                ctx.shadowBlur = 0;\n            });\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制食物\n        function drawFood() {\n            const x = food.x * GRID_SIZE;\n            const y = food.y * GRID_SIZE;\n            \n            // 食物发光效果\n            ctx.shadowColor = '#ff6b6b';\n            ctx.shadowBlur = 15;\n            \n            // 绘制圆形食物\n            ctx.fillStyle = '#ff6b6b';\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(\n                x + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                y + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                GRID_SIZE / 2 - 2,\n                0,\n                Math.PI * 2\n            );\n            ctx.fill();\n            \n            // 重置阴影\n            ctx.shadowBlur = 0;\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制边界\n        function drawBoundary() {\n            ctx.strokeStyle = '#4fd1c5';\n            ctx.lineWidth = 3;\n            ctx.strokeRect(1, 1, CANVAS_WIDTH - 2, CANVAS_HEIGHT - 2);\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制圆角矩形\n        function drawRoundedRect(x, y, width, height, radius) {\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.moveTo(x + radius, y);\n            ctx.lineTo(x + width - radius, y);\n            ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x + width, y, x + width, y + radius);\n            ctx.lineTo(x + width, y + height - radius);\n            ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x + width, y + height, x + width - radius, y + height);\n            ctx.lineTo(x + radius, y + height);\n            ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x, y + height, x, y + height - radius);\n            ctx.lineTo(x, y + radius);\n            ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x, y, x + radius, y);\n            ctx.closePath();\n        }\n        \n        // 键盘输入处理\n        function handleKeyDown(event) {\n            const key = event.key;\n            \n            switch (key) {\n                case 'ArrowUp':\n                    if (direction !== DIRECTIONS.DOWN) {\n                        nextDirection = DIRECTIONS.UP;\n                    }\n                    event.preventDefault();\n                    break;\n                case 'ArrowDown':\n                    if (direction !== DIRECTIONS.UP) {\n                        nextDirection = DIRECTIONS.DOWN;\n                    }\n                    event.preventDefault();\n                    break;\n                case 'ArrowLeft':\n                    if (direction !== DIRECTIONS.RIGHT) {\n                        nextDirection = DIRECTIONS.LEFT;\n                    }\n                    event.preventDefault();\n                    break;\n                case 'ArrowRight':\n                    if (direction !== DIRECTIONS.LEFT) {\n                        nextDirection = DIRECTIONS.RIGHT;\n                    }\n                    event.preventDefault();\n                    break;\n                case ' ':\n                    if (gameState === GAME_STATES.PLAYING) {\n                        pauseGame();\n                    } else if (gameState === GAME_STATES.PAUSED) {\n                        resumeGame();\n                    }\n                    event.preventDefault();\n                    break;\n                case 'r':\n                case 'R':\n                    if (gameState === GAME_STATES.GAMEOVER || gameState === GAME_STATES.PAUSED) {\n                        startGame();\n                    }\n                    event.preventDefault();\n                    break;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 开始游戏\n        function startGame() {\n            // 重置游戏状态\n            gameState = GAME_STATES.PLAYING;\n            score = 0;\n            updateInterval = 150;\n            \n            // 重置蛇\n            snake = [\n                { x: Math.floor(GRID_COUNT_X / 2), y: Math.floor(GRID_COUNT_Y / 2) },\n                { x: Math.floor(GRID_COUNT_X / 2) - 1, y: Math.floor(GRID_COUNT_Y / 2) },\n                { x: Math.floor(GRID_COUNT_X / 2) - 2, y: Math.floor(GRID_COUNT_Y / 2) }\n            ];\n            \n            // 重置方向\n            direction = DIRECTIONS.RIGHT;\n            nextDirection = DIRECTIONS.RIGHT;\n            \n            // 生成食物\n            generateFood();\n            \n            // 更新UI\n            document.getElementById('scoreValue').textContent = score;\n            hideAllMessages();\n            \n            // 重置更新时间\n            lastUpdateTime = performance.now();\n        }\n        \n        // 暂停游戏\n        function pauseGame() {\n            if (gameState === GAME_STATES.PLAYING) {\n                gameState = GAME_STATES.PAUSED;\n                showMessage('pauseMessage');\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 恢复游戏\n        function resumeGame() {\n            if (gameState === GAME_STATES.PAUSED) {\n                gameState = GAME_STATES.PLAYING;\n                hideAllMessages();\n                lastUpdateTime = performance.now();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏结束\n        function gameOver() {\n            gameState = GAME_STATES.GAMEOVER;\n            \n            // 更新最终得分\n            document.getElementById('finalScore').textContent = score;\n            document.getElementById('finalHighScore').textContent = highScore;\n            \n            showMessage('gameOverMessage');\n        }\n        \n        // 显示消息\n        function showMessage(messageId) {\n            hideAllMessages();\n            document.getElementById(messageId).style.display = 'block';\n        }\n        \n        // 隐藏所有消息\n        function hideAllMessages() {\n            document.querySelectorAll('.game-message').forEach(msg => {\n                msg.style.display = 'none';\n            });\n        }\n        \n        // 启动游戏\n        window.addEventListener('load', init);\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
